try%20and%20its%20leading%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20likely%20there%20will%20be%20relief%20for%20the%20sector%20anytime%20soon.%20At%20least%2C%20that's%20what%20policymakers%20are%20signaling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Binance%20chief%20Changpeng%20Zhao%20joined%20his%20former%20industry%20rival%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20in%20making%20headlines%20for%20charges%20against%20him%20and%20his%20crypto%20exchange%2C%20which%20included%20breaching%20US%20anti-money-laundering%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbinance-ceo-cz-guilty-plea-department-of-justice-money-laundering-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZhao%20pleaded%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20left%20his%20role%20as%20CEO.%20Binance%20is%20set%20to%20pay%20over%20%244.3%20billion%20in%20fines%2C%20%2450%20million%20of%20which%20will%20be%20paid%20by%20the%20former%20CEO%20himself.%20A%20portion%20of%20that%20will%20go%20to%20settle%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%20for%20allowing%20US%20customers%20to%20trade%20unregistered%20crypto%20derivatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20made%20by%20CFTC%20Commissioner%20Christy%20Goldsmith%20Romero%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20pirate%20ships%20in%20US%20markets%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Baccess%20to%20US%20customers%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%20not%20a%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldsmith%20added%20that%20the%20CFTC%20plans%20to%20continue%20its%20aggressive%20pursuit%20of%20crypto%20exchanges%20that%20violate%20trade%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commissioner%20noted%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20tolerance%20for%20using%20VPNs%2C%20or%20any%20other%20actions%20that%20could%20circumvent%20KYC%20rules%2C%20including%20pop-up%20questions%20that%20merely%20ask%20users%20to%20attest%20that%20they%20aren't%20based%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20statement%2C%20CFTC%