0is%20virtual%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%20the%20members%20have%20already%20agreed%20on%20their%20quotas%2C%20and%20the%20meeting%20will%20be%20a%20short%20formality%2C%20he%20said.%20It%20also%20coincides%20with%20the%20COP28%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20which%20many%20ministers%20will%20be%20attending%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20levels%20at%20which%20production%20can%20be%20pulled%20back%3A%20through%20OPEC%2B%2C%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20existing%20voluntary%20cuts%2C%20and%20new%20voluntary%20cuts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20should%20expect%20production%20cutbacks%20from%20OPEC%2B%2C%20and%20on%20the%20voluntary%20level%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20its%20allies%20extending%20into%20January%20or%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20Alhajji%20noted.%20This%20is%20because%20demand%20seasonally%20declines%20in%20the%20first%20quarter.%20But%2C%20what%20he%20anticipates%20could%20happen%20is%20an%20announcement%20about%20additional%20voluntary%20cuts%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20all%20of%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20Alhajji%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20believe%20that%20the%20only%20way%20the%20Saudis%20can%20be%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20in%20the%20oil%20market%20without%20anyone%20else%20with%20them%20is%20if%20we%20are%20in%20backwardation%2C%20where%20today's%20prices%20are%20way%20higher%20than%20the%20following%20month's%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20it's%20the%20opposite%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20futures%20market%20is%20in%20contango%2C%20which%20means%20futures%20contracts%20are%20higher%20than%20current%20prices.%20This%20incentivizes%20investors%20and%20companies%20to%20store%20oil%2C%20causing%20inventories%20to%20rise.%20If%20Saudi%20Arabia%20does%20implement%20additional%20cuts%2C%20then%20this%20will%20flip%20the%20futures%20curve%20into%20backwardation%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F