London%20described%20his%20life%20as%20a%20nightmare.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20the%20army%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20their%20capabilities%20to%20get%20them%20back.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmily%20was%20initially%20believed%20to%20be%20among%20the%201%2C200%20Israelis%20killed%20during%20the%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20in%20southern%20Israel.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%20counted%20among%20the%20240%20hostages%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20sole%20purpose%20in%20life%20now%20is%20to%20do%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20get%20my%20little%20daughter%20Emily%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hand%2C%20who%20after%20living%20in%20Be'eri%20kibbutz%20for%2020%20years%20working%20in%20a%20printing%20house%2C%20now%20lives%20in%20a%20hotel%20near%20the%20Dead%20Sea.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20else%20concerns%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20on%20its%20Facebook%20page%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20beautiful%208-year-old%20girl%20Emily%20Hand%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20murdered%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20on%20October%207th.%20We%20now%20know%20she%20is%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza.%20Please%20share%20this%20and%20help%20us%20bring%20Emily%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FIsraelMFA%252Fvideos%252F314271228058272%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D264%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20deal%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20a%20four-day%20truce%20so%20that%2050%20women%20and%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20taken%20hostage%20could%20be%20freed%20in%20return%20for%20150%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20teenage