ied-rise-and-fall-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20crypto-billionaire%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20learn%20the%20economic%20system%20of%20New%20York's%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disgraced%20founder%20of%20crypto%20exchange%20FTX%20has%20reportedly%20been%20keeping%20busy%20by%20swapping%20food%20items%20in%20exchange%20for%20services%20as%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjury-sam-bankman-fried-guilty-seven-counts-fraud-manhattan-trial-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawaits%20sentencing%20on%20seven%20felony%20counts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20include%20wire%20fraud%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20know%20that%20the%20new%20polished%20haircut%20he%20has%20been%20seen%20with%20in%20New%20York%20courtrooms%20is%20thanks%20to%20an%20inmate.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Fcurrencies%2Fsam-bankman-frieds-life-behind-bars-crypto-tips-and-paying-with-fish-858097c6%3Fst%3Dqlb7okwrhbjcjof%26reflink%3Darticle_copyURL_share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20SBF%20paid%20for%20a%20haircut%20with%20packaged%20mackerel%2C%20a%20type%20of%20pelagic%20fish%20that%20is%20a%20choice%20of%20currency%20among%20inmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20former%20trader%20would%20quickly%20catch%20on%20to%20the%20commodity%20of%20choice%20in%20his%20new%20environment.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20professional%20trader%20for%20much%20of%20his%20career.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20got%20his%20first%20intern%20gig%20at%20Jane%20Street%20Capital%2C%20swapping%20exchange-traded%20funds%20before%20co-founding%20his%20crypto%20trading%20firm%20Alameda%20Research%20in%202017.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20he%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20arbitrage%20bitcoin%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Japanese%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fish%2C%20popularly%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bmacks%26quot%3B%20among%20inmates%2C%20has%20been%20the%20choice%20of%20currency%20in%20federal%20prisons%20since%202004%2C%20after%20cigarettes%20were%20banned%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormerly%20incarcerated%20attorney%20Larry%20Levin%20accepted%20it%20as%20a%20form%20of%20payment%20from%20fellow%20prisoners%20he%20represented%20while%20serving%20his%20own%20sentence%20at%20the%20Lompoc%20correctional%20institution%20in%20California.%20He%20then%20used%20them%20to%20pay%20for%20personal%20upkeep%20services%20such%20as%20beard%20trims%20and%20shoe%20shines%20from%20inmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20became%20so%20popular%20that%20Global%20Source%20Marketing%2C%20a%20supplier%20of%20the%20fish%2C%20felt%20the%20increased%20demand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FSB122290720439096481%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%202008%20story%20from%20the%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20economic%20logic%20behind%20the%20trend.%20Products%20that%20have%20steady%20value%20such%20as%20certain%20food%20items%20and%20stamps%20are%20used%20as%20a%20steady%20means%20of%20exchange%20to%20substitute%20for%20currency%2C%20which%20inmates%20cannot%20access.%20Food%20items%20like%20mack%20and%20tuna%20are%20stable%20commodities%20with%20a%20value%20that%20can%20be%20pegged%20to%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20be%20sentenced%20on%20March%2028%2C%202024%2C%20faces%20up%20to%20110%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20the%20fraud%20charges%20brought%20against%20him%2C%20but%20it's%20only%20part%20of%20the%20charges%20he%20is%20facing.%20He%20is%20also%20set%20to%20stand%20trial%20for%20separate%20counts%20related%20to%20political%20bribery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftx-ftx-trading-fish-in-prison-for-servi