%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20AI's%20impact%20will%20be%20as%20dramatic%20as%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%2C%20but%20it%20certainly%20will%20be%20as%20big%20as%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20PC.%20Word%20processing%20applications%20didn't%20do%20away%20with%20office%20work%2C%20but%20they%20changed%20it%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gates%20said%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BEmployers%20and%20employees%20had%20to%20adapt%2C%20and%20they%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20risks%20of%20AI%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bmisinformation%20and%20deepfakes%2C%20security%20threats%2C%20changes%20to%20the%20job%20market%2C%20and%20the%20impact%20on%20education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20new%20technology%20has%20caused%20a%20big%20shift%20in%20the%20labour%20market.%20I%20don't%20think%20AI's%20impact%20will%20be%20as%20dramatic%20as%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%2C%20but%20it%20certainly%20will%20be%20as%20big%20as%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20PC%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20thing%20that's%20clear%20to%20me%20is%20that%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20is%20not%20as%20grim%20as%20some%20people%20think%20or%20as%20rosy%20as%20others%20think.%20The%20risks%20are%20real%2C%20but%20I%20am%20optimistic%20that%20they%20can%20be%20managed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700755980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F28nkia78_bill-gates-reuters_625x300_10_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-foresees-a-3-day-work-week-thanks-to-ai-4600908%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2068-year-old%20Microsoft%20co-founder%20said%20that%20AI%20will%20not%20be%20taking%20jobs%20but%20will%20%26quot%3Bchange%20it%20forever.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22h