onist's%20vehicle%20was%20implicated%20in%20transporting%20beef%20and%20further%20recorded%20that%20since%20the%20revisionist%20failed%20to%20provide%20convincing%20evidence%20contradicting%20the%20claim%2C%20the%20vehicle%20was%20liable%20to%20be%20confiscated%20under%20the%20anti-cow%20slaughter%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20restrictions%20on%20transportation%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20Act%20and%20the%20rules%20framed%20thereunder%20are%20only%20applicable%20in%20respect%20of%20transportation%20of%20cow%2C%20bull%20or%20bullock%2C%20that%20too%20in%20any%20place%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20from%20any%20place%20outside%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20on%20Monday%20after%20hearing%20the%20lawyers%20from%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20entire%20Act%20or%20the%20rules%2C%20there%20exists%20no%20provision%20barring%20transportation%20of%20beef.%20The%20restriction%20placed%20under%20section%205A%20of%20the%20cow%20slaughter%20Act%20is%20only%20in%20respect%20of%20transportation%20of%20cow%2C%20bull%20or%20bullock%2C%20that%20too%20only%20from%20a%20place%20outside%20the%20state%20to%20any%20place%20within%20the%20state.%20There%20is%20no%20bar%20or%20restriction%20on%20transportation%20of%20beef%20even%20from%20any%20place%20outside%20the%20state%20to%20any%20place%20inside%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20alleged%20transportation%20of%20beef%20on%20a%20vehicle%20(motorcycle)%20within%20two%20places%20in%20the%20state%20is%20neither%20prohibited%20nor%20even%20regulated%20and%20thus%2C%20the%20foundation%20for%20confiscation%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20transportation%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20this%20Act%20is%20prima%20facie%20not%20established%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20holding%20that%20the%20power%20of%20confiscation%20has%20been%20exercised%20without%20any%20authority%20of%20law%20and%20on%20a%20misreading%20of%20section%205A(7)%20of%20the%20cow%20slaughter%20Act%2C%20and%20for%20the%20said%20reasons%2C%20the%20confiscation%20order%20cannot%20be%20sustained%20and%20is%20liable%20to%20be%20quashed%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700754600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fj0c9ekio_allahabad-high-court-_625x300_14_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-anti-cow-slaughter-law-doesnt-ban-transportation-of-beef-allahabad-high-court-4600869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prevention%20of%20Cow%20Slaughter%20Act%20does%20not%20prohibit%20the%20transportation%20of%20beef.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-anti-cow-slaughter-law-doesnt-ban-transportation-of-beef-allahabad-high-court-4600869%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-anti-cow-slaughter-law-doesnt-ban-transportation-of-beef-allahabad-high-court-4600869%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-anti-cow-slaughter-law-doesnt-ban-transportation-of-beef-allahabad-high-court-4600869%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lithuanian%20president%20demands%20'punishment'%20for%20Russian%20book%20thefts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700754357000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105452735%2Cimgsize-850025.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Flithuanian-president-demands-punishment-for-russian-book-thefts%2Far