e%20taekwondo.%20I%20politely%20said%20that%20strength%20matters%20more%20than%20physical%20appearance.%20I%20was%20not%20like%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20my%20god%2C%20sir%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20willpower%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20too%20senior%3B%20they%20understand%20when%20you%20are%20not%20being%20yourself.%20They%20do%20not%20appreciate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Mandla%20District%20Collectorate%20Facebook%2C%20Saloni%20Sidana%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700747920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Saloni%20Sidana%20pursued%20civil%20services%20after%20completing%20her%20MBBS.%20She%20aced%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%2074th%20rank%20in%20her%20first%20attempt.%20Serving%20as%20Mandla's%20district%20collector%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20she%20recently%20went%20viral%20for%20spending%20only%20Rs%20500%20on%20her%20wedding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334751%2Fias-officer-saloni-sidana-shares-strategy-for-cracking-upsc-cse-in-first-attemptsaloni-sidana-upsc-cse-in-first-attempt-district-collector-mandla-madhya-pradesh-wedding%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhanush%20Biopic%20on%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%3A%20The%20Real%20Story%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Musical%20Sage%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIlaiyaraaja%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298846%2Fponniyin-selvan-must-watch-mani-ratnam-movies-yuva-alaipayuthey-nayakan-indian-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprolific%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20has%20seen.%20The%20composer%20has%