26quot%3Bdhoks%26quot%3B%20or%20shelters%20for%20graziers%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20army%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20area%20after%20receiving%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20locals%20and%20had%20started%20operations%20in%20Ziarat%2C%20Mal%2C%20Gulabgarh%20forest%20and%20the%20Solaki%20Area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20MV%20Pranjal%20of%2063%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20was%20the%20first%20to%20get%20shot%20while%20talking%20to%20an%20elderly%20woman%20to%20gather%20information%20in%20the%20area%20where%20the%20terrorists%20were%20hiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesperate%20to%20get%20the%20injured%20Captain%20to%20safety%2C%20Major%20DS%20Mehra%20of%209%20Para%20went%20into%20the%20area%2C%20drawing%20fire%20from%20the%20terrorists%20and%20sustaining%20a%20gunshot%20wound.%C2%A0%20Captain%20Pranjal%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20though%20Major%20Mehra%20has%20been%20evacuated%20and%20is%20recovering%20from%20his%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20went%20in%20to%20support%20Major%20Mehra%20were%20Captain%20Shubham%20Gupta%2C%20Havildar%20Abdul%20Majid%20and%20Lance%20Naik%20Sanjay%20Bisht%2C%20all%20from%209%20Para%20Special%20Forces.%C2%A0%20Captain%20Gupta%20and%20two%20jawans%20were%20fatally%20injured%20as%20they%20tried%20to%20tactically%20intervene.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20morning%2C%20Pakistan%20attempted%20to%20drop%20arms%20to%20the%20terrorists%20by%20drones%2C%20an%20attempt%20which%20has%20been%20foiled.%20The%20drones%20were%20carrying%20ammunition%2C%20which%20have%20been%20recovered%2C%20and%20probably%20pistols%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%209%20am%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20was%20killed%20but%20another%20soldier%2C%20Paratrooper%20Sachin%20Laur%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20action%20during%20the%20operation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20terrorist%2C%20who%20was%20hiding%20behind%20a%20Sangar%20(stone%20structures%20in%20the%20forest)%20and%20firing%20int