.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-how-the-encounter-in-jammu-and-kashmir-unfolded-4600149%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Prakash%20Raj%20Summoned%20In%20Rs%20100-Crore%20Ponzi%20Scam%20Linked%20To%20Jeweller%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Prakash%20Raj%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20100-crore%20Ponzi%20scheme%20linked%20to%20a%20jeweller.%20Mr%20Raj%20was%20the%20brand%20ambassador%20of%20Pranav%20Jewellers%2C%20a%20chain%20accused%20of%20running%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20raided%20branches%20of%20the%20Trichy-based%20jewellery%20chain%2C%20which%20has%20branches%20in%20several%20places%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%2C%20including%20Chennai%2C%20for%20allegedly%20running%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme%20and%20duping%20investors%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20who%20had%20been%20the%20brand%20ambassador%20of%20the%20jeweller%20for%20a%20significant%20period%2C%20has%20not%20given%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stores%20run%20by%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20shut%20down%20in%20October%20and%2C%20based%20on%20complaints%2C%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Trichy%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20owner%2C%20Madhan.%20Lookout%20notices%20had%20also%20been%20issued%20against%20the%20owner%20and%20his%20wife%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20in%20a%20statement%20yesterday%20said%20Rs%20100%20crore%20had%20been%20collected%20by%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20gold%20investment%20scheme%20that%20promised%20high%20returns.%20Not%20only%20did%20the%20returns%20not%20materialise%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20invested%20had%20also%20not%20been%20given%20back%20to%20the%20investors%2C%20the%20ED%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPranav%20Jewellers%20failed%20to%20return%20the%20amount%20to%20such%20investors%20and%20the%20firm%20(Pranav%20Jewellers)%20and%20other%20connected%20persons%20cheated%20the%20public%20by%20diverting%20public%20funds%20to%20shell%20entities%2Fentry%20providers%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20purchase%20of%20bullion%2Fgold%20ornaments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20supplier%20parties%20in%20the%20books%20of%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20were%20entry%20providers%2C%20who%20during%20the%20investigation%2C%20%26quot%3Bconfessed%26quot%3B%20to%20providing%20adjustment%20and%20bogus%20accommodation%20entries%20to%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20for%20amount%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20and%20also%20%26quot%3Bconfessed%26quot%3B%20to%20giving%20cash%20to%20the%20accused%20persons%20in%20lieu%20of%20bank%20payments%2C%20the%20ED%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700746260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2F3m0m3lgs_prakash-raj-pti_625x300_10_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-prakash-raj-summoned-in-rs-100-crore-ponzi-scam-linked-to-jeweller-4600185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Prakash%20Raj%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20100-crore%20Ponzi%20scheme%20linked%20to%20a%20jeweller.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-prakash-raj-summoned-in-rs-100-crore-ponzi-scam-linked-to-jeweller-4600185%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-prakash-raj-summoned-in-rs-100-crore-ponzi-scam-linked-to-jeweller-4600185%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-prakash-raj-summoned-in-rs-100-crore-ponzi-scam-linked-to-jeweller-4600185%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EU%20sends%20border%20police%20reinforcements%20to%20Finland%20over%20fears%20that%20Russia%20