onal%20efficiency%2C%20and%20establish%20new%20benchmarks%20for%20performance%20and%20environmental%20sustainability%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdefence-shipyard-grse-to-develop-electric-tugs-e-volt-50-with-partners-123112300789_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdefence-shipyard-grse-to-develop-electric-tugs-e-volt-50-with-partners-123112300789_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdefence-shipyard-grse-to-develop-electric-tugs-e-volt-50-with-partners-123112300789_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Customer%20data%20shared%20with%20account%20aggregators%20totally%20safe%3A%20FM%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700743160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F06%2Ffull%2F1699293666-5979.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcustomer-data-shared-with-account-aggregators-totally-safe-fm-sitharaman-123112300779_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Account%20aggregators%20(AA)%20are%20entities%20that%20enable%20financial%20data%20sharing%20from%20Financial%20Information%20Providers%20(FIPs)%20to%20Financial%20Information%20Users%20(FIUs)%2C%20based%20on%20the%20consent%20from%20the%20customers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcustomer-data-shared-with-account-aggregators-totally-safe-fm-sitharaman-123112300779_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Revdi%20Culture%20-%20%26quot%3BThe%20New%20Normal%26quot%3B%20In%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETen%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20in%20politics.%20During%20this%20time%20India%20has%20witnessed%20a%20new%20political%20paradigm.%20Modern%20India%2C%20since%20the%20time%20of%20Independence%2C%20has%20not%20straitjacketed%20itself%20into%20an%20ideological%20narrative%2C%20like%20many%20countries%20did%20after%20freeing%20themselves%20from%20the%20colonial%20powers.%20India%20was%20broadly%20governed%20by%20a%20few%20stray%20thoughts%20like%20secularism%2C%20modernism%2C%20federalism%2C%20democracy%2C%20scientific%20temper%20and%20pluralism.%20India%20was%20more%20a%20mosaic%20of%20many%20cultures%20and%20there%20never%20was%20a%20fear%20that%20followers%20of%20a%20particular%20faith%20or%20culture%20would%20face%20subordination%20by%20the%20dominant%20culture.%20Since%202014%2C%20India%20has%20blossomed%20into%20an%20ideological%20state%20and%20Hindutva%20has%20become%20the%20dominant%20creed.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202014%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20use%20Hindutva%20as%20a%20major%20mobilising%20tool%3B%20the%20'Gujarat%20model'%20of%20economic%20development%20was%20packaged%20into%20an%20attractive%20alternative%20to%20the%20Congress's%20corruption.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Hindutva%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20formidable%20tool%20for%20winning%20elections%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Modi%20cult.%20Now%20it%20seems%20that%20narrative%20may%20be%20losing%20its%20charm.%20The%20politics%20of%20freebies%20-%20%3Cem%3Erevdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20culture%20-%20is%20becoming%20the%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavishing%20freebies%20on%20voters%20is%20not%20new%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20experimented%20with%20this%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades.%20North%20India%2C%20however%2C%20is%20just%20wising%20up%20to%20its%20potency%20in%20winning%20elections.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20deserves%20credit%20for%20this.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)'s%20unprecedented%20success%20in%202013%20was%20ascribed%20to%20the%20promise%20to%20Delhi%20voters%20that%20they%20would%20get%20up%20to%20200%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%20would%20be%20supplied%20at%20half%20the%20price.%20Within%20a%20year%20of%20its%20formation%2C%20AAP%20decimated%20Sheila%20Dixit's%20Congress%20in%20Delhi%20and%20won%2028%20seats.%20After%20forming%20the%20government%2C%20Kejriwal%20implemented%20both%20the%20schemes%2C%20which%20became%20AAP's%20calling%20card%2C%20and%20led%20him%20to%20superlative%20victories%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Modi%2C%20after%20becoming%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20did%20launch%20the%20Ujjwala%20scheme%20to%20provide%20free%20gas%20stoves%20(%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20people%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%20But%20schemes%20like%20this%20and%20many%20others%20were%20categorised%20as%20welfare%20schemes.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20political%20analysts%20used%20a%20new%20descriptor%20-%20%3Cem%3ELabharthi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20beneficiary%20class%20-%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20a%20new%20social%20base%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Opposition%20parties%20struggled%20to%20counter%20Modi's%20brilliant%20combination%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20did%20realise%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20successfully%20painted%20them%20as%20anti-Hindu%20and%20pro-Muslim.%20In%20a%20country%20where%20more%20than%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%20is%20Hindu%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dangerous%20prospect%20for%20any%20party%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20anti-Hindu.%20No%20wonder%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20after%20becoming%20Congress%20president%2C%20was%20seen%20temple-hopping%20with%20fervour.%20He%20even%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20showing%20his%20%3Cem%3EJaneu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20sacred%20thread%20worn%20by%20Brahmins.%20It%20did%20pay%20off%3B%20the%20BJP%20struggled%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%20at%20bay%20and%20win%20the%20Gujarat%20election.%20The%20party%20could%20not%20win%20a%20majority%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20lost%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20But%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Pulwama%20terror%20attack%20and%20India's%20retaliatory%20air%20strikes%20targeting%20terror%20training%20camps%20in%20Pakistan's%20Balakot%2C%20Modi%20returned%20with%20a%20bang%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%202019%2C%20political%20parties%20avoided%20being%20seen%20with%20Muslims.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20when%20Muslims%20were%20being%20targeted%20by%20right%20wing%20Hindutva-vadis.%20Left%20orphaned%20by%20the%20political%20parties%20and%20discriminated%20against%20by%20law%20enforcing%20agencies%2C%20Muslims%20were%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves.%20This%20was%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20opposition%20to%20appropriate%20the%20politics%20of%20Hindutva.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20seen%20livestreaming%20his%20Diwali%20Puja.%20If%20he%20recited%20the%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%20then%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20proudly%20chanted%20the%20Gayatri%20Mantra%20during%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20election.%20Rahul%2C%20Kejriwal%20or%20Mamta%2C%20all%20proclaimed%20themselves%20to%20be%20proud%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Kamal%20Nath%20both%20tried%20to%20project%20themselves%20as%20Hindu%20leaders.%20This%20drew%20criticism%20from%20a%20section%20of%20left%20liberals%20who%20accused%20them%20of%20chasing%20Hindutva%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20new%20political%20narrative%20was%20rearing%20its%20head.%20The%20Congress%20had%20tasted%20blood%20when%20its%20promise%20of%20upto%20300%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20and%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20women%20(aged%2018%20to%2060%20years)%20every%20month%2C%20along%20with%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%20helped%20them%20win%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20Congress%20repeated%20similar%20guarantees%20in%20Karnataka.%20It%20promised%20200%20units%20of%20free%20power%2C%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20every%20family%2C%2010%20kg%20free%20rice%20to%20each%20member%20of%20the%20state's%20poorest%20families%2C%20Rs%203%2C000%20a%20month%20to%20graduates%20and%20Rs%201%2C500%20for%20diploma%20holders.%20The%20cost%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer%20was%20estimated%20to%20be%20approximately%20Rs%2062%2C000%20crore.%20The%20Congress%20routed%20the%20BJP%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20Karnataka%20victory%20created%20a%20new%20template%20for%20the%20Congress.%20The%20BJP%20was%20rattled.%20PM%20Modi%20called%20the%20freebies%20culture%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20for%20development%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2016%20July%202023%2C%20Modi%20said%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jalaun%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20country%20today%2C%20attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20bring%20a%20culture%20of%20garnering%20votes%20by%20distributing%20%3Cem%3Erevdis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20%3Cem%3Erevdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20culture%20is%20very%20dangerous%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country.%20People%20of%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20the%20youth%2C%20need%20to%20guard%20against%20this%20culture.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20by%20the%20same%20Modi%20is%20driven%20to%20hand%20out%20%3Cem%3Erevdis%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20elections%20in%20five%20states.%20When%20the%20Congress%20promised%20a%20gas%20cylinder%20at%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20women%20every%20month%2C%20the%20BJP%20promptly%20announced%20Rs%201%2C250%20per%20month%20for%20women%20under%20the%20%26quot%3BLadli%20Behna%20Yojana%26quot%3B%20and%20gas%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20450%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Ujjwala%20and%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana.%20Like%20Himachal%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Congress%20again%20promised%20up%20to%20100%20units%20of%20free%20power%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20announced%20it%20would%20provide%20gas%20cylinders%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%20450%20to%20counter%20the%20Congress's%20earlier%20promise%20of%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20the%20Congress%20revised%20its%20own%20promise%20and%20announced%20that%20now%20it%20would%20give%20cooking%20gas%20at%20Rs%20400.%20If%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20Congress%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20distributed%20laptops%20to%20young%20graduates%20and%20free%20mobile%20phones%20to%20girls%2C%20the%20BJP%20promised%20free%20scooties%20for%20girl%20students%2C%20and%20copying%20the%20Congress%20promise%20of%20free%20education%20up%20to%20graduation%20for%20all%20students%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%20promised%20to%20make%20%26quot%3BKG%20to%20PG%20free%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20an%20economist%20so%20I%20am%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20speculate%20whether%20the%20freebies%20culture%20will%20be%20detrimental%20to%20the%20country%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%3B%20but%20this%20clearly%20indicates%20that%20a%20new%20political%20narrative%20is%20emerging%20and%20it%20might%20overwhelm%20the%20BJP.%20No%20doubt%2C%20Hindutva%20has%20given%20a%20cutting%20edge%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP.%20It%20has%20helped%20the%20party%20to%20not%20only%20consolidate%20its%20ideological%20base%20structure%20but%20has%20also%20attracted%20new%20voters%20and%20helped%20enhance%20the%20organisation's%20super%20structure.%20It%20has%20definitely%20created%20a%20new%20electoral%20social%20class%20that%20does%20not%20carry%20the%20baggage%20of%20secularism%20and%20proudly%20asserts%20its%20Hindu%20moorings.%20This%20'new'%20class%20might%20not%20be%20anti-Muslim%20in%20its%20ethos%20but%20it%20definitely%20wears%20its%20'Hinduness'%20on%20its%20sleeve.%20It%20is%20this%20Hindu%20who%20is%20not%20ideologically%20committed%20to%20RSS's%20Hindutva%2C%20who%20can%20be%20attracted%20to%20the%20freebies%20and%20shift%20preference%20due%20to%20the%20perceived%20lack%20of%20economic%20delivery%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20states%20and%20also%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20the%20voters%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202014%2C%20because%2C%20in%20a%20fast-changing%20technological%20age%2C%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20New%20Society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20know%20it%20is%20too%20early%20for%20conclusions%20but%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20miss%20the%20shift.%20Those%20who%20imagine%20that%20the%20life%20span%20of%20Hindutva%20politics%20is%20short%2C%20prepare%20to%20be%20hugely%20disappointed.%20Hindutva%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20but%20the%20'aspirational'%20Hindu%2C%20who%20gave%20the%20BJP%20a%20cutting%20edge%2C%20may%20chart%20a%20new%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreebies%20is%20just%20a%20hint%20of%20the%20disappointment.%20As%20I%20said%2C%2010%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20in%20politics%2C%20therefore%2C%20now%20is%20the%20time%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20re-orient%20its%20socio-political%20and%20politico-economic%20strategy.%20It's%20the%20era%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20voter's%20mind%20is%20not%20artificial.%20It%20does%20not%20need%20a%20machine%20to%20think%20for%20themselves.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20creative%20thinking.%20Political%20parties%20including%20the%20BJP%20need%20to%20understand%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700743140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fabfq7b5_cylinder_625x300_12_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frevdi-culture-the-new-normal-in-elections-4600082%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lavishing%20freebies%20on%20voters%20is%20not%20new%20in%20Indian%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonic