0an%20unfortunate%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnoopnautiyal1%2Fstatus%2F1726620226291392885%5C%22%3Eunforeseeable%20natural%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20assertion%20is%20disingenuous%20and%20risible.%20The%20collapse%20was%20anything%20but%20unforeseeable.%20Countless%20locals%2C%20activists%20and%20academics%20had%20warned%20against%20pell-mell%20construction%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20stressing%20their%20fragility%20and%20instability.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fenvironmentalist-ravi-chopra-resigns-as-chairman-of-sc-appointed-committee-on-char-dham-road%2Farticleshow%2F89487286.cms%5C%22%3ERavi%20Chopra%20committee%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20just%20one%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Silkyara%20and%20the%20larger%20project%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fenvironment%2Fchar-dham-highway-project-uttarakhand-technical-loophole-escape-environmental-scrutiny%5C%22%3EChar%20Dham%20Mahamarg%20Pariyojana%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20notable%20is%20the%20planners%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20ignore%20these%20warnings.%20This%20decision%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20tells%20us%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20clearance%20architecture%20is%20now%20fully%20broken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwho-was-building-the-uttarakhand-tunnel-that-collapsed%5C%22%3EWho%20Was%20Building%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%20That%20Collapsed%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20went%20wrong%20with%20Silkyara%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20backstory%20here%20is%20well-known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fenvironment%2Fchar-dham-highway-project-uttarakhand-technical-loophole-escape-environmental-scrutiny%5C%22%3EChar%20Dham%20Mahamarg%20Pariyojana%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeks%20to%20build%20wide%2C%20all-weather%20roads%2C%20between%20the%20Hindu%20holy%20towns%20of%20Gangotri%2C%20Yamunotri%2C%20Badrinath%20and%20Kedarnath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20India%2C%20once%20beyond%20a%20stipulated%20threshold%2C%20have%20to%20get%20themselves%20an%20environmental%20clearance.%20Any%20proposed%20highway%20running%20longer%20than%20100%20kilometres%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20needs%20an%20environmental%20clearance.%20Given%20it%20is%20900%20km%2C%20Char%20Dham%20needed%20one%20as%20well.%20In%20a%20rush%20to%20finish%20the%20project%20before%20the%20next%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20split%20the%20project%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fchar-dham-highway-project-shouldve-undergone-impact-assessment-v-k-saraswat%5C%22%3E53%20separate%20sections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20none%20over%20100%20km%20in%20length%2C%20and%20evaded%20the%20need%20for%20an%20environmental%20impact%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20that%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20when%20this%20ball%20started%20rolling.%20A%20better%20starting%20point%20is%202013%2C%20when%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20decided%20to%20waive%20environmental%20clearances%20for%20road%20projects%20less%20than%20100%20km%20long.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20the%20NDA%20made%20use%20of%20this%20waiver%20even%20though%20the%20Main%20Himalayan%20Thrust%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20Indian%20plate%20pushes%20under%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20runs%20through%20Uttarakhand%20but%20comes%20close%20to%20the%20tunnel%20site.%20This%2C%20as%20activist%20Himanshu%20Thakkar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fopinion%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-collapse-at-what-point-will-we-wake-up-to-the-himalayan-disasters-11793081.html%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20creates%20obvious%20%E2%80%9Cseismic%20and%20shear%20zone%20implications%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinding%20no%20room%20for%20their%20concerns%20in%20this%20abbreviated%20planning%20process%2C%20locals%20approached%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-approves-centres-char-dham-project-only-new-projects-need-environment-clearance%2Farticleshow%2F67491413.cms%5C%22%3ENational%20Green%20Tribunal%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-approves-centres-char-dham-project-only-new-projects-need-environment-clearance%2Farticleshow%2F67491413.cms%5C%22%3Eand%20the%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-approves-centres-char-dham-project-only-new-projects-need-environment-clearance%2Farticleshow%2F67491413.cms%5C%22%3En%2C%20the%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-approves-centres-char-dham-project-only-new-projects-need-environment-clearance%2Farticleshow%2F67491413.cms%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Cour%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-approves-centres-char-dham-project-only-new-projects-need-environment-clearance%2Farticleshow%2F67491413.cms%5C%22%3Et%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20sidestepping%20of%20the%20environmental%20clearance%20process%20went%20unchallenged%20by%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20these%20cases%20were%20being%20heard%2C%20the%20project%20rolled%20on.%20In%20February%202018%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1521024%5C%22%3Eapproved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Barkot-Silkyara%20tunnel%20%E2%80%93%20between%20Gangotri%20and%20Yamunotri.%20In%20June%202018%2C%20the%20state-owned%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20(NHIDCL)%20awarded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-highlights-himalayan-fragility-and-the-need-for-escape-routes%5C%22%3Ethe%20tender%20for%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-highlights-himalayan-fragility-and-the-need-for-escape-routes%5C%22%3Etunnel%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Hyderabad-based%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20year%2C%20Navayuga%20hired%20a%20German-Austrian%20engineering%20consultancy%20called%20Bernard%20Gruppe%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bernard-gruppe.com%2Fen%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fsilkyara-tunnel%2F%5C%22%3Edesign%20and%20build%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20Sikkim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20before%20Silkyara%2C%20geological%20risks%20had%20hammered%20another%20infrastructure%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sikkim%2C%20a%20glacial%20lake%20burst%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20Teesta%20punching%20its%20way%20through%201%2C200%20megawatt%20Teesta%20III%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x166.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679982%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22566%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20devastated%E2%80%9D%20dam%20site%20area%20of%20Teesta-III.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%20%40shubhamtorres09%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Teesta%20III%20and%20Silkyara%20are%20analogous%20tales.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20dam%2C%20locals%E2%80%99%20warnings%20about%20glacial%20lakes%20had%20been%20ignored.%20As%20a%20forthcoming%20story%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20show%2C%20its%20construction%20was%20handed%20out%20to%20an%20untested%20firm%20which%20was%20just%20four%20months%20old%20when%20it%20bagged%20the%20tender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20the%20dam%20management%20failed%20to%20enshrine%20disaster%20management%20and%20dam%20safety%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20what%20happened%20thereafter.%20Geological%20risks%20%E2%80%93%20ignored%20during%20the%20environmental%20clearance%20process%20%E2%80%93%20asserted%20themselves%20once%20construction%20started.%20The%20dam%20site%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20landslide%20and%20then%20by%20an%20earthquake.%20Both%20resulted%20in%20construction%20delays%2C%20and%20left%20the%20hydel%20project%20unviable.%20Then%20came%20the%20glacial%20flood%2C%20and%20took%20the%20dam%20out%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20at%20Silkyara%20has%20traced%20a%20similar%20trajectory.%20Once%20construction%20began%2C%20Navayuga%20ran%20into%20geological%20surprises.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20start%20of%20tunnel%20driving%2C%20the%20geological%20conditions%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20more%20challenging%20than%20predicted%20in%20the%20tender%20documents%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bernard%20Gruppe%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bernard-gruppe.com%2Fen%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fsilkyara-tunnel%2F%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20Navayuga%20took%20a%20series%20of%20decisions%20which%20amplified%20workers%E2%80%99%20vulnerability%20to%20geological%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20glaring%20of%20these%20decisions%20was%20the%20failure%20to%20build%20an%20escape%20passage%2C%20as%20stipulated%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1521024%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20cabinet%20approval%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20if%20the%20company%20wanted%20to%20build%20such%20a%20passage%20%E2%80%93%20for%20travellers%20%E2%80%93%20only%20after%20completing%20the%20main%20tunnel%2C%20it%20needed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frapiduplift%2Fstatus%2F1726440504173453735%5C%22%3Ebuild%20an%20escape%20route%20for%20workers%20in%20the%20case%20of%20an%20emergency%20during%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESo%20many%20red%20flags%20in%20the%20Uttarkashi%20tunnel%20construction%20project.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHVrLjDu0E7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHVrLjDu0E7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Suvrat%20Kher%20(%40rapiduplift)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frapiduplift%2Fstatus%2F1726440504173453735%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20omission%20went%20unchallenged%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%3B%20by%20NHIDCL%3B%20and%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways.%20It%20stayed%20unchallenged%20even%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fsamruddhi-expressway-accident-sub-contractors-booked-crane-collapse-kills-8871230%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20accident%20at%20another%20Navayuga%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fsamruddhi-expressway-accident-sub-contractors-booked-crane-collapse-kills-8871230%2F%5C%22%3Eproject%20site%20this%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fconstruction-workers-dead-in-thane-after-girder-falls-on-sam