2Fkhichdi-in-bottles-1st-hot-meal-for-trapped-uttarakhand-tunnel-workers-in-9-days-4590699%5C%22%3Esix-inch%20pipe%20was%20eventually%20pushed%20through%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20workers%2C%20did%20they%20get%20their%20first%20cooked%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20preparation%20drew%20flak%20from%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20commencing%20work%20on%20such%20projects%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20have%20safety%20protocols%20in%20place%20and%20also%20have%20rescue%20plans%20in%20case%20of%20emergencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fhemant-soren-slams-central-government-over-tunnel-mishap-in-uttarkashi%2Fcid%2F1981922%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20situation%20is%20that%20even%20after%20so%20many%20days%2C%20there%20are%20talks%20of%20hiring%20foreign%20experts%20for%20rescue%20works.%20We%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20wait.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20asked%20Navayuga%20why%20the%20escape%20tunnel%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20built%2C%20if%20it%20had%20used%20explosives%2C%20and%20why%20it%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20planned%20for%20contingencies%20despite%20multiple%20warnings%20about%20the%20Himalayas%20being%20fragile%20and%20unstable.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20it%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%2C%20however%2C%20scratch%20the%20surface.%20Silkyara%20(and%20Teesta%20III)%20are%20proverbial%20canaries%20in%20a%20mine%2C%20giving%20us%20a%20deeper%20warning%20than%20just%20the%20specific%20infirmities%20of%20these%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sikkim-cm-cannot-evade-responsibility-on-the-teesta-dam-breach%5C%22%3EThe%20Sikkim%20CM%20Cannot%20Evade%20Responsibility%20on%20the%20Teesta%20Dam%20Breach%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ceded%20landscape%20of%20environmental%20protections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20May%206%2C%202020%2C%20history%20repeated%20itself%20in%20Vizag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%203%20am%20that%20night%2C%20a%20neuro-toxic%20gas%20leaked%20from%20a%20chemical%20plant%20of%20LG%20Polymers%20and%20spread%20into%20the%20colonies%20abutting%20the%20plant.%20Thirty-six%20years%20after%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%2C%20Indians%20again%20woke%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvizag-factory-chemical-gas-leak-victim-account-recounts-horror-breathlessness-burning-eyes%5C%22%3Estruggling%20to%20breath%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvizag-factory-chemical-gas-leak-victim-account-recounts-horror-breathlessness-burning-eyes%5C%22%3Ee%2C%20their%20eyes%20b%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvizag-factory-chemical-gas-leak-victim-account-recounts-horror-breathlessness-burning-eyes%5C%22%3Eurning%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20least%2011%20people%20died%20in%20the%20incident.%20About%205%2C000%20were%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20it%20emerged%20that%20the%20plant%20had%20been%20running%20without%20an%20environmental%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20sobering%20moment.%20After%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%2C%20India%20passed%20new%20laws%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Factsofparliamentfromtheyear%2Fenvironment-protection-act-1986%5C%22%3EEnvironment%20Protection%20Act%20(EPA)%2C%201986%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Factsofparliamentfromtheyear%2Fpublic-liability-insurance-act-1991%5C%22%3EPublic%20Liability%20Insurance%20Act%20(PLIA)%2C%201991%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20amended%20existing%20ones%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Factsofparliamentfromtheyear%2Ffactories-act-1948%5C%22%3EFactories%20Act%2C%201948%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20public%20costs%20of%20industries%20working%20with%20hazardous%20technologies%20and%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20these%20laws%20too%20were%20weakened%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20night%20in%20Vizag%2C%20the%20full%20scale%20of%20usurped%20environmental%20protections%20became%20suddenly%20visible.%20As%20%3Cem%3EArticle-14%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.article-14.com%2Fpost%2Findia-is-back-to-a-time-before-the-bhopal-gas-tragedy%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20poisonous%20gas%20leaks%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fgross-negligence-lack-of-training-caused-vizag-gas-leak-report-1683735-2020-05-30%5C%22%3Epoorly%20maintained%3C%2Fa%3E%20industrial%20unit%2C%20operating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2020%2F05%2Fyears-of-neglect-led-to-vizag-gas-tragedy%2F%5C%22%3Ewithout%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20environmental%20clearance%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20residential%20neighbourhoods%2C%20it%20invites%20more%20than%20comparisons%20with%20Union%20Carbide.%20It%20forces%20the%20belated%20recognition%20that%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20effective%20protection%20against%20industrial%20pollution%2C%20India%20is%20back%20where%20she%20was%20before%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F07103316%2F2020_5img07_May_2020_PTI07-05-2020_000012B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F07103316%2F2020_5img07_May_2020_PTI07-05-2020_000012B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F07103316%2F2020_5img07_May_2020_PTI07-05-2020_000012B-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F07103316%2F2020_5img07_May_2020_PTI07-05-2020_000012B-1024x667.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-453117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22782%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20being%20treated%20at%20a%20hospital%20after%20a%20major%20chemical%20gas%20leakage%20at%20LG%20Polymers%20industry%20in%20RR%20Venkatapuram%20village%2C%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Thursday%2C%20May%2007%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20Videograb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20big%20warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20big%20lesson%20from%20Silkyara%20and%20Teesta%20III%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20time%2C%20seeking%20to%20protect%20places%20like%20Silent%20Valley%2C%20India%20created%20a%20strong%20environmental%20governance%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%2030%20years%2C%20however%2C%20a%20double%20movement%20has%20played%20out.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20country%20rolled%20out%20large%20infrastructure-building%20drives%20%E2%80%93%20to%20set%20up%20thermal%20power%20projects%2C%20erect%20dams%2C%20build%20highways%2C%20set%20up%20ports.%20In%20tandem%2C%20given%20industrial%20lobbying%20for%20deregulation%20and%20the%20gravy%20train%20around%20infrastructure-building%2C%20the%20country%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.article-14.com%2Fpost%2Findia-is-back-to-a-time-before-the-bhopal-gas-tragedy%5C%22%3Eweakened%20its%20environmental%20governance%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20cynical%20game.%20For%20over%2020%20years%2C%20the%20environment%20ministry%20has%20been%20presented%20as%20a%20roadblock%2C%20delaying%20the%20construction%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20plants%20and%20infrastructure%20projects.%20The%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcompany%2Fcorporate-trends%2Findia-inc-unhappy-over-delays-in-green-nods-by-environment-minister-jayanthi-natarajan%2Farticleshow%2F18438096.cms%5C%22%3Ewas%20also%20presented%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fed-attaches-15-properties-of-a-raja-under-pmla-act%2Farticle67404846.ece%5C%22%3Eas%20corrupt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20successive%20ministers%20taking%20bribes%20to%20clear%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fix%20these%20problems%2C%20the%20country%20needed%20to%20insulate%20project%20approvals%20from%20inefficiency%20and%20political%20interference.%20One%20solution%20was%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fpolicy%2Fenvironment-clearance-as-patronage%2Farticleshow%2Fmsid-5434996%2Ccurpg-2.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ea%20statutory%20environment%20regulator%20like%20America%E2%80%99s%20Environment%20Protection%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20would%20also%20do%20away%20with%20politicians%E2%80%99%20power%20to%20issue%20environment%2Fforest%20clearances.%20This%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20Instead%2C%20successive%20governments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.article-14.com%2Fpost%2Findia-is-back-to-a-time-before-the-bhopal-gas-tragedy%5C%22%3Eweakened%20India%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20clearance%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Public%20hearings%20were%20defanged%3B%20project%20proponents%20were%20allowed%20to%20define%20the%20environmental%20parameters%20along%20which%20their%20projects%20would%20be%20evaluated%3B%20the%20time%20taken%20to%20evaluate%20projects%20was%20slashed%3B%20one%20could%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chickens%20are%20now%20coming%20home%20to%20roost.%20In%20both%20Teesta%20III%20and%20Silkyara%2C%20policy%20plans%20and%20project%20reports%20barely%20acknowledged%20environmental%20risks.%20In%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20the%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20was%20cursory.%20In%20the%20second%2C%20there%20was%20no%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20geological%20risks%20showed%20up%20during%20construction.%20All%20of%20this%20raises%20a%20large%20question.%20Over%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20new%20double%20movement%20of%20fresh%20infrastructure%20projects%20(river-interlinking%2C%20inland%20waterways%2C%20more%20highways%E2%80%A6)%20while%20continuing%20to%20weaken%20India%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20laws.%20The%20resulting%20interplay%20%E2%80%93%20between%20disregarded%20environmental%20risks%20and%20infrastructure%20projects%20%E2%80%93%20has%20to%20be%20better%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20here%20is%20that%20the%20resulting%20costs%20are%20unfairly%20distributed.%20At%20Silkyara%2C%2041%20workers%20came%20close%20to%20losing%20their%20lives.%20In%20the%20days%20after%20Teesta%20III%E2%80%99s%20collapse%2C%20social%20media%20was%20filled%20with%20images%20of%20locals%20trying%20to%20save%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2C%20however%2C%20are%20highly%20visible%20instances%20of%20planning%20failures.%20Others%20are%20more%20invisible.%20Poorly%20scrutinised%20risks%20result%20in%20cost-%20and%20time%20overruns%2C%20turning%20projects%20unviable%2C%20even%20forcing%20states%20to%20support%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20are%20the%20costs%20of%20looking%20at%20environmental%20protections%20as%20barriers%20for%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.%20Rajshekhar%20is%20an%20independent%20reporter%20studying%20corruption%2C%20oligarchy%2C%20and%20the%20political%20economy%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%3Cem%3Es%20environment.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FDespite-State-India-Lets-People%2Fdp%2F8194879019%2F%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20State%3A%20Why%20India%20Lets%20Its%20People%20Down%20and%20How%20They%20Cope%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700742644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20225721%2FF_TZ16gaYAARVxR.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-warning-environment-development%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20relief%20that%20the%20trapped%20workers%20will%20soon%20be%20rescued%2C%20India%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20forget%20the%20key%20warning%20from%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20system%20is%20broken.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-warning-environment-development%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trapped%20Workers%20Will%20Be%20Rolled%20Out%20On%20Stretchers%20From%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20forty-one%20workers%20who%20are%20trapped%20under%20a%20collapsed%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20will%20be%20pulled%20out%20on%20wheeled%20stretchers%20one%20by%20one%20through%20a%20big%20pipe%20that%20is%20still%20being%20drilled%20to%20reach%20them%2C%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20Director%20General%20Atul%20Karwal%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescuers%20had%20also%20considered%20the%20option%20of%20making%20the%20workers%20crawl%20out%20one%20by%20one.%20Their%20health%20condition%2C%20however%2C%20may%20prevent%20them%20from%20crawling%20out%20on%20their%20own%2C%20following%2012%20days%20of%20living%20under%20the%20debris%20of%20the%20tunnel%20without%20any%20natural%20light%20and%20full%20meals%2C%20though%20they%20have%20been%20given%20supplies%20via%20small%20%26quot%3Blifeline%26quot%3B%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDRF%20personnel%20will%20slide%20in%20through%20the%20pipe%20and%20once%20they%20reach%20the%20workers%2C%20they%20will%20use%20the%20stretchers%20to%20send%20out%20workers%20one%20by%20one%2C%20Mr%20Karwal%20said%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20worker%20will%20be%20made%20to%20lie%20low%20on%20the%20stretcher%20to%20prevent%20their%20limbs%20from%20scrapping%20the%20welded%20pipe's%20metal%20underside%20while%20NDRF%20personnel%20pull%20the%20stretcher%20with%20a%20rope%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescue%20operation%20to%20bring%20out%20the%2041%20workers%20trapped%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20resumed%20this%20morning%20after%20an%20iron%20mesh%20that%20had%20come%20in%20the%20path%20of%20the%20auger%20machine%20drilling%20an%20escape%20path%20was%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F1cv3qs8_uttarakhand-tunnel_625x300_22_November_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20800-mm%20diameter%20rescue%20pipe%20will%20be%20cleaned%20by%20the%20NDRF%20and%20its%20state%20counterpart%20to%20ensure%20no%20debris%20prevents%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20stretchers%2C%20Mr%20Karwal%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20pipe%20is%20wide%20enough%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20800-mm%20pipes%20have%20a%20width%20of%20nearly%2032%20inches%2C%20which%20is%20enough.%20Even%20if%20we%20get%20a%20width%20of%2022-24%20inches%2C%20we%20can%20pull%20out%20people%20through%20them.%20Our%20men%20have%20carried%20out%20rehearsals%20for%20the%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Karwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20auger%20machine%20drills%20through%2C%20pipes%20are%20being%20pushed%20through%20the%20debris.%20Once%20a%20pipe%20is%20all%20in%2C%20another%20is%20welded%20to%20it.%20In%20this%20manner%2C%20the%20escape%20route%20is%20being%20prepped%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%20out%20of%20their%20long%20confinement.%20Welders%20have%20been%20flown%20in%20from%20Delhi%20to%20put%20together%20the%20final%20stretch%20of%20the%20pipe.%20They%20will%20get%20to%20work%20once%20the%20drilling%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20pipe%20is%20being%20welded%20now.%20We%20plan%20to%20drill%20two%20more%20pipes%20now%20so%20that%20we%20achieve%20a%20length%20of%20up%20to%2060%20metres%20through%20the%20rubble%20to%20get%20some%20extended%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Karwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDRF%20chief%20said%20Uttarakhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20talked%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers%20and%20they%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20good%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20work%20in%20tunnels%20are%20mentally%20tough%20and%20they%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20huge%20efforts%20being%20carried%20out%20to%20evacuate%20them.%20So%20they%20are%20optimistic%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Karwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202-km%20section%20of%20the%20tunnel%20where%20concrete%20work%20has%20been%20completed%20is%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20rescue%20efforts%20as%20this%20secured%20section%20has%20electricity%2C%20water%20supply%20and%20a%20new%20six-inch-diameter%20pipe%20to%20deliver%20cooked%20food%20and%20medicines%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20existing%20four-inch-diameter%20lifeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20second%20lifeline%2C%20the%20trapped%20workers%20are%20being%20given%20foods%20like%20roti%2C%20subzi%2C%20khichdi%2C%20daliya%2C%20oranges%20and%20bananas%2C%20and%20medicines%20and%20other%20essentials%20such%20T-shirts%2C%20undergarments%2C%20toothpaste%20and%20soap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700742300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fm53m9vao_uttarakhand-tunnel_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F41-workers-to-be-pulled-out-on-stretchers-from-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-says-ndrf-official-4599975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20forty-on