mpanies%2Fnews%2Fcoal-india-to-phase-out-mining-equipment-imports-in-6-years-says-govt-123112300699_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcoal-india-to-phase-out-mining-equipment-imports-in-6-years-says-govt-123112300699_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekar's%20Exotic%20Car%20Collection%20To%20Be%20Auctioned%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20end%20and%20luxury%20vehicles%20owned%20by%20jailed%20alleged%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekar%20will%20be%20auctioned%20next%20week%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20in%20Bengaluru%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20recover%20the%20dues%20he%20owes%20to%20several%20institutions%2C%20sources%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IT%20department%20sources%2C%2011%20such%20cars%20and%20a%20bike%20would%20be%20up%20for%20e-auction%20on%20November%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cars%20which%20would%20be%20up%20for%20auction%20are%20BMW%20M5%2C%20Toyota%20Prado%2C%20Range%20Rover%2C%20Lamborghini%2C%20Jaguar%20XKR%20Coupe%2C%20Rolls%20Royce%2C%20Bentley%2C%20Innova%20Crysta%2C%20Toyota%20Fortuner%2C%20Nissan%20Teana%20and%20Porsche.%20Besides%20these%2011%20cars%2C%20the%20IT%20department%20would%20also%20be%20auctioning%20his%20(Sukesh's)%20sports%20cruiser%20bike%20-%20Ducati%20Diavel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20department%2C%20sources%20said%20the%20price%20of%20these%20vehicles%20ranges%20from%20Rs%202.03%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201.74%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20vehicles%20seized%20by%20the%20department%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20including%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20be%20auctioned%20online.%20At%20present%2C%20these%20vehicles%20stated%20to%20be%20in%20%26quot%3Bgood%20condition%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20department%20have%20been%20kept%20at%20Central%20Revenue%20building%20for%20inspection%20till%20Friday%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20claimed%20that%20as%20of%20November%2010%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20owes%20Rs%20308.48%20crore%20dues%20to%20various%20government%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20vehicles%20owned%20by%20Sukesh%20were%20seized%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20including%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20year%202018%20by%20the%20IT%20department.%20He%20owes%20dues%20worth%20several%20crores%20(of%20rupees)%20to%20various%20government%20institutions%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20recover%20those%20dues%20by%20putting%20these%20high%20end%20vehicles%20for%20auction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrashekhar%20who%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20a%20Delhi%20Jail%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20impersonating%20top%20government%20officials%20in%20order%20to%20extort%20about%20Rs%20200%20crore%20from%20Aditi%20Singh%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Shivinder%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20the%20former%20owner%20of%20pharma%20major%20Ranbaxy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20conman%20was%20claimed%20to%20have%20scammed%20Aditi%20Singh%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20securing%20the%20release%20of%20her%20husband%20who%20was%20in%20jail%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20is%20also%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700742240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2Fo86ohdqo_sukesh-chandrashekhar-extortion-hawala-racket_625x300_04_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjailed-sukesh-chandrashekars-high-end-vehicles-to-be-auctioned-by-it-department-in-bengaluru-4599514%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cars%20which%20would%20be%20up%20for%20auction%20are%20BMW%20M5%2C%20Toyota%20Prado%2C%20Range%20Rover%2C%20Lamborghini%2C%20Jaguar%20XKR%20Coupe%2C%20Rolls%20Royce%2C%20Bentley%2C%20Innova%20Crysta%2C%20Toyota%20F