racts%20the%20public%20by%20raising%20topics%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%2C%20demonetisation%2C%20and%20GST.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Adani%20comes%20from%20behind%20and%20takes%20the%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20took%20exception%20to%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20against%20PM%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CCalling%20any%20person%20for%20that%20instance%20a%20Jaibkatra%20not%20only%20amounts%20to%20vicious%20abuse%20and%20personal%20attack%20but%20also%20a%20character%20assassination%20of%20that%20person%20against%20whom%20such%20remark%20has%20been%20made%20with%20a%20clear%20intent%20to%20harm%20his%20reputation%20and%20mislead%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJP%20had%20said%20in%20its%20complaint%20filed%20before%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700740230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26210652%2FFufcgtmX0AQCmkG.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-serves-notice-to-rahul-gandhi-over-panauti-remark-against-pm-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20called%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20'panauti%20(harbinger%20of%20bad%20luck)'%2C%20linking%20India's%20loss%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20final%20to%20the%20latter's%20presence%20at%20the%20Ahmedabad%20stadium.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-serves-notice-to-rahul-gandhi-over-panauti-remark-against-pm-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22XpressBees%20joins%20ONDC%20networks%2C%20expands%20services%20to%2020%2C000%20pin%20codes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700740226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F07%2Ffull%2F1699365989-8382.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2