ing%20the%20Dutch%20elections!%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fviktor-orban%2Ft-38337120%5C%22%3EHungarian%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20far-right%20leader%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Rassemblement%20National%20party%2C%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CCongratulations%20to%20Geert%20Wilders%20and%20the%20PVV%20for%20their%20spectacular%20performance%20in%20the%20legislative%20elections%20which%20confirms%20the%20growing%20attachment%20to%20the%20defense%20of%20national%20identities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItalian%20far-right%20leader%20and%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20Matteo%20Salvini%20also%20congratulated%20Wilders.%20%E2%80%9CCongratulations%20to%20our%20friend%20Geert%20Wilders%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20PVV%20and%20historic%20ally%20of%20the%20League%2C%20for%20this%20extraordinary%20electoral%20victory.%20A%20new%20Europe%20is%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnxiety%20about%20the%20election%20results%20is%20growing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20also%20expressed%20trepidation%20over%20the%20election%20outcome.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Feu-climate-chief-we-need-to-be-more-ambitious%2Fa-59629194%5C%22%3EFrans%20Timmermans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Green%2FLabor%20left-wing%20bloc%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CDemocracy%20has%20spoken%2C%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20for%20us%20to%20defend%20democracy%2C%20to%20defend%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20a%20fist%20against%20exclusion%2C%20against%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20distress%20and%20fear%20are%20enormous%E2%80%A6%20Wilders%20is%20known%20for%20his%20ideas%20about%20Muslims%20and%20Moroccans.%20We%20are%20afraid%20that%20he%20will%20portray%20us%20as%20second-class%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib%20El%20Kaddouri%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Dutch%20organization%20representing%20Dutch-Moroccans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20Finance%20Minister%20Bruno%20Le%20Maire%20said%20Wilders%E2%80%99%20election%20victory%C2%A0was%20a%20consequence%20of%20%E2%80%9Call%20the%20fears%20that%20are%20emerging%20in%20Europe%E2%80%9D%20over%20immigration%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Geert%20Wilders%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Dutch%20Trump%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgeert-wilders%2Ft-38265771%5C%22%3EGeert%20Wilders%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20anti-Islam%2C%20anti-immigrant%20and%20anti-EU%20message%20seems%20to%20have%20finally%20swept%20him%20to%20first%20place%20at%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20calling%20Moroccans%20%E2%80%9Cscum%E2%80%9D%20to%20holding%20competitions%20for%20cartoons%20of%20the%20Prophet%20Mohammed%2C%20Wilders%20has%20built%20a%20career%20from%20his%20self-appointed%20mission%20to%20stop%20an%20%E2%80%9CIslamic%20invasion%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20remained%20defiant%20despite%20brushes%20with%20the%20law%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20convicted%20for%20insulting%20Moroccans%20%E2%80%93%20and%20death%20threats%20that%20have%20meant%20he%20has%20been%20under%20police%20protection%20since%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201963%20in%20southern%20Venlo%2C%20close%20to%20the%20German%20border%2C%20Wilders%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20Catholic%20family%20with%20his%20brother%20and%20two%20sisters.%20His%20mother%20was%20half-Indonesian%2C%20a%20fact%20Wilders%20rarely%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilders%20entered%20politics%20in%201998%20in%20the%20Liberal%20VVD%20party%2C%20before%20beginning%20a%20one-man%20faction%20in%20parliament%20and%20then%20forming%20the%20far-right%20PVV%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgeert-wilders-far-right-populist-wins-big-in-dutch-election%2Fa-67528159%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20publishe