n%20official%20said%20something%20both%20smart%20and%20wise%20about%20peacemaking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20decades%2C%20he%20said%2C%20even%20before%20the%20Franco-German%20war%20of%201870-71%2C%20every%20generation%20of%20Germans%20and%20the%20French%20knew%20they%20would%20be%20going%20to%20war%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20they%20inevitably%20did.%20It%20was%20only%20through%20a%20peace%20agreement%20after%20World%20War%20II%20that%20this%20ended.%20Given%20this%20history%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20tell%20Indians%20and%20Pakistanis%2C%20except%20that%20he%20hoped%20we%20would%20be%20smarter%20than%20the%20Europeans%20and%20find%20a%20pathway%20to%20peace%20faster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20later%2C%20again%20in%20Berlin%2C%20an%20Israeli%20journalist%20told%20me%20about%20how%20she%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20tasked%20with%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20framework%20for%20dealing%20with%20the%20complicated%20issue%20of%20Jerusalem.%20This%20was%20part%20of%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20informal%20group%20brought%20together%20by%20civil%20society.%20She%20had%2C%20she%20said%2C%20been%20very%20sceptical%20that%20something%20so%20deeply%20polarising%20even%20in%20such%20an%20unofficial%20group%20could%20be%20discussed%20fruitfully.%20But%20over%20three%20days%20of%20intense%20discussion%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20what%20they%20thought%20was%20a%20workable%20proposal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20mention%20this%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20recent%20proposal%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20hostage%20exchange%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20Most%20commentators%2C%20rightly%2C%20emphasise%20that%20this%20is%20far%20from%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20also%20highlighted%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20further%20from%20any%20prospect%20of%20peace.%20While%20this%20is%20true%2C%20we%20must%20always%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20reason%20that%20peace%20is%20elusive%20is%20not%20because%20it%20is%20impossible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeace%20is%20always%20possible%2C%20and%20even%20the%20most%20contentious%20issues%20can%20be%20worked%20out.%20The%20only%20real%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20principal%20political%20actors%20are%20sincerely%20willing%20to%20work%20towards%20peace%2C%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20hard%20decisions%20required%20to%20mean%20that%20it%20is%20a%20real%2C%20honourable%2C%20and%20durable%20peace.%20But%20once%20that%20is%20in%20place%2C%20even%20the%20most%20difficult%20issues%20seem%20to%20disappear%20so%20completely%20it%20is%20as%20if%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20for%20hostility%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20region%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fplace%2FAlsace-Lorraine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAlsace-Lorraine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20was%20the%20principal%20bone%20of%20contention%20of%20the%20Franco-German%20War%20of%201870-71%2C%20and%20continued%20to%20be%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20war%20until%20World%20War%20II%20has%20been%20totally%20peaceful%20since%201945.%20A%20small%20region%20over%20whose%20control%20Germany%20and%20France%20expended%20countless%20lives%20and%20brought%20the%20world%20to%20war%20now%20has%20borders%20so%20porous%20between%20both%20countries%20that%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20cross%20them%20without%20realising%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20will%20point%20to%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20the%20rise%2C%20fall%20and%20horrors%20of%20the%20Nazi%20regime%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20terrible%20destruction%20that%20World%20War%20I%20and%20World%20War%20II%20inflicted%20on%20Europe%20as%20the%20motivating%20reason%20for%20the%20long%20peace.%20Again%2C%20this%20is%20true%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20that%20the%20Germans%20and%20the%20French%20could%20not%20have%20figured%20out%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20to%20the%20dispute%20before%20all%20of%20this.%20That%20they%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20millions%20over%20seven%20decades%20of%20warfare%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20could%20share%20the%20land%20without%20feeling%20threatened%20is%20an%20indictment%20of%20European%20thinking%20and%20war-mongering.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20justification%20for%20the%20lives%20lost%20and%20ruined%20over%20such%20a%20long%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Israel-Palestine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20any%20number%20of%20conflicts%20around%20the%20world%2C%20we%20are%20told%20the%20horrors%20that%20people%20have%20lived%20through%20and%20the%20unspeakable%20crimes%20committed%20by%20various%20sides%2C%20make%20peace%20impossible.%20This%20is%20only%20an%20excuse%20for%20more%20war%2C%20for%20more%20misery.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20is%20clear%20about%20the%20terrible%20costs%20of%20war%20on%20ordinary%20people%20is%20the%20absolute%20necessity%20that%20such%20horrors%20do%20not%20happen%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWar%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20often%20a%20choice%20that%20leads%20to%20more%20war.%20Let%20us%20not%20seek%20to%20excuse%20the%20political%20leaders%20for%20the%20bad%20choices%20they%20make%20by%20suggesting%20that%20peace%20is%20impossible.%20It%20is%20never%20true.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700733374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03120804%2Fisrael-palestine.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-peace-is-always-possible%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22War%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20often%20a%20choice%20that%20leads%20to%20more%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-pal