112512%2FThe-Wire-86.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAround%205%20lakh%20Sahara%20Group%20investors%20are%20planning%20to%20stage%20a%20huge%20protest%20demonstration%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20December%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20demand%20the%20return%20of%20the%20money%20that%20they%20had%20invested%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20death%20of%20Group%20founder%20Subrata%20Roy%20on%20November%2014%2C%20there%20is%20a%20heightened%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20and%20urgency%20on%20the%20part%20of%20investors%20who%20are%20spread%20across%2027%20states%20across%20the%20country.%20With%20the%20portal%20launched%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20July%20to%20facilitate%20the%20refunds%20yet%20to%20take%20off%20and%20the%20allegations%20against%20authorities%20that%20claims%20are%20being%20rejected%20on%20%E2%80%9Cfrivolous%20grounds%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20consternation%20among%20lakhs%20of%20investors%20who%20fear%20that%20their%20money%20would%20be%20transferred%20to%20Consolidated%20Fund%20of%20India%20in%20the%20name%20of%20unclaimed%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%20Dev%20Shukla%2C%20president%20of%20a%20registered%20body%20representing%20the%20Sahara%20investors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fabout-five-lakh-sahara-group-investors-to-protest-in-delhi-against-governments-failure-to-refund-their-deposits%2Farticle67562508.ece%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20if%20the%20government%20confiscated%20the%20Sahara%20chairperson%E2%80%99s%20property%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20money%20of%20crores%20of%20investors%20will%20be%20lost%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20tolerated%20at%20any%20cost%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20December%2C%20depositors%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20will%20reach%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20and%20will%20%3Ci%3Egherao%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E(surround)%20