r%20the%20world%2C%20he%20also%20endeavoured%20to%20leave%20behind%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%2C%20and%20more%20sustainable%20world%20for%20her.%20Today%2C%20he%20owns%20The%20EleFant%20%E2%80%94%20a%20toy%20rental%20company%2C%20or%20in%20Sourabh%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20labour%20of%20love%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20major%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Indore%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20etc.%20Curious%20about%20how%20the%20business%20works%20and%20how%20you%20can%20rent%20toys%20for%20your%20kids%3F%20Read%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%2C%20age-appropriate%20and%20fun%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Sourabh%20always%20had%20an%20entrepreneurial%20mindset.%20Despite%20working%20as%20a%20chartered%20accountant%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life%2C%20he%20harboured%20a%20persistent%20interest%20in%20starting%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EleFant%20emerged%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20toys%20for%20my%20daughter%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20brand%20for%20parents%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-500x262.jpg%20500w%