-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-300x232.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-500x386.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-768x593.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-150x116.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334519%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERukhsaar%20innovates%20different%20dishes%20using%20traditional%20Kashmiri%20ingredients.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Khalis%20Foods%20is%20thriving%2C%20Rukhsaar%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20audition%20for%20MasterChef%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20talk%20about%20Kashmiri%20cuisine%2C%20they%20talk%20about%20%3Cem%3Ewazwan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Erogan%20josh%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Through%20MasterChef%20India%2C%20I%20want%20the%20country%20to%20know%20how%20we%20prepare%20homemade%20food%20in%20Kashmir.%20We%20use%20so%20many%20local%20indigenous%20ingredients%20to%20make%20our%20food%20and%20there%20is%20a%20science%20behind%20every%20ingredient%20used.%20The%20world%20must%20know%20Kashmiri%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98ghar%20ka%20khana%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshe%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERukhsaar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20eight%20finalists%20in%20MasterChef%20India-Hindi%20and%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Kashmiri%20women%20on%20the%20show.%20She%E2%80%99s%20been%20%E2%80%98wow%E2%80%99ing%20the%20judges%20with%20her%20dishes%2C%20where%20she%20uses%20traditional%20Kashmiri%20ingredients%20in%20creative%2C%20restaurant-quality%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20chef%20thanks%20to%20MasterChef.%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ve%20done%20it%20all%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20one%20of%20the%20few%20Kashmiri%20women%20chefs%2C%20Rukhsaar%20is%20a%20beacon%20of%20inspiration%20for%20young%20girls%20in%20the%20valley.%20She%20urges%20youngsters%20to%20follow%20their%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20career%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20my%20passion%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20youngsters%20to%20look%20at%20ways%20to%20transform%20their%20passion%20into%20a%20career.%20Have%20faith%20in%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20her%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98aha%20%3C%2Fem%3Emoment%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20day%20she%20felt%20%E2%80%98she%20made%20it%E2%80%99%2C%20despite%20achieving%20so%20much%2C%20Rukhsaar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20day%20is%20yet%20to%20come%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20a%20good%20place%20and%20very%20grateful%20for%20everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20received%20so%20far.%20But%20I%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20do.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20truly%20ever%20wanted%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20wait%20to%20see%20the%20heights%20that%20this%20fiery%20woman%20reaches%2C%20you%20can%20follow%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkhalis_foods%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20place%20orders%2C%20or%20just%20be%20a%20bystander%20to%20witness%20her%20incredible%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700568317000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2